We all know the classic Tetris theme, based on Korobeiniki... but what if it got harder and HARDER? This awesome piano version of the Tetris theme will take you through 20 incredible levels of the most mind-bending and insane piano music ever written. All in one video. All on one theme. Do you think you have what it takes to play this piano arrangement of the Tetris theme? Let us know in the comments...
